      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, then take your <strong>chicken </strong>out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Add a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> to a large <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>(or two!)</p><p>Add your <strong>diced chicken breast</strong> to one side of the dish[es]</p><p>Coat your<strong> gnocchi</strong> in a little<strong> olive oil</strong> and add it to the other side of the dish[es]</p>",
